pt">consumers</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> to find a regulated financial </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">adviser</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> who can advise on their care funding needs</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> in their area</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">, if they so wish</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">4.4</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">A</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">s a consequence of referring self</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">-</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">funders to financial information,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> not only is the citizen enabled to make better informed decisions</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> about how</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> to fund their care needs, </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">but it also </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">help</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> local authorities prevent self</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">-</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">funders from depleting their</sp